{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban the police from strip searching children and replace with doctor examination",
        "additional_details": "The government must change the policy that gives the police the right to strip search children. In the event that an intrusive search is necessary, it should be done by a medical professional qualified to do the examination.",
        "background": "Remove the right to strip search minors from the police and replace child strip searches with examinations by doctors.",
